        Configures the first filter of a given type, if multiple are available.
        Equivalent to 
         
 T filter = getFirstFilterByClass(clazz);
 if(filter != null) {
      configurator.accept(filter);
 }
        Type Parameters:
        T - Filter type.
        Parameters:
        clazz - Filter class, used for internal lookup.
        configurator - Configurator for the filter. Will be called one time at most.
